The following are components of a perforated border. The stride gap and depth blocks below are default settings that can be overridden in a parent of the block containing the perforation attribute
<stride=6/>
<gap=12/>
<depth=2/>
<perfRight> d gap l depth d stride r depth;</perfRight>
<perfLeft>r depth u stride l depth u gap;</perfLeft>
<perfTop>u depth r gap d depth r stride;</perfTop>
<perfBottom>u depth l stride d depth l gap;</perfBottom>
The perforation block draws the perforation.
<perforation drawPath fill=$perfColor border selectable=no>%@ 0 u~ 8 perfLeft 5 perfTop 5 u depth r 10 d 2 perfRight 5 d 8 l 10 perfBottom 5;</perforation>

